u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15409,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/allah-teaches-adam-salaam\/","url_meta":{"origin":33688,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Allah teaches Adam greeting of peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah created Adam in His image, sixty cubits tall. When He created him, Allah said: Go and greet these groups of assembled angels with peace and listen to how they greet you, for this will be the greeting\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32215,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/16\/allah-is-salaam-spread-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":33688,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Allah\u2019s name is peace, so spread peace on earth","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 16, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, peace is among the names of Allah that He has placed on the earth, so spread it between yourselves. If a man greets people with peace and they answer him, he is favored by\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15419,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/gabriel-greet-peace\/","url_meta":{"origin":33688,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Jibreel: Angel Gabriel greets you with peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said to her, \u201cO Aisha, here is the Angel Gabriel to greet you with peace.\" Aisha said, \"And upon him be peace, the mercy of Allah, and His blessings. You see what I do not see.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6249,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":42157,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2024\/08\/22\/signposts-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":33688,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Signposts on the Straight Path","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 22, 2024","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Islam has milestones, lamps like the lamps on the road. Among them are that you worship Allah without associating anything with Him, you perform the prayer, you give charity, you perform the Hajj pilgrimage to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":12947,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/03\/18\/four-rakaat-before-asr\/","url_meta":{"origin":33688,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Sunan: Four raka&#8217;at of prayer before &#8216;Asr","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 18, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ali ibn Abi Talib reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, would pray four cycles before afternoon prayer, separating them with the invocation of peace upon the favored angels and those who follow them among the Muslims and believers. Al-Tirmidhi said, \"Ibrahim ibn Ishaq preferred not to separate\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33688","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33688"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33688\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33688"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-